<HEADLINE> Tehran Stock Index Rises by 8.07 Points </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
TEHRAN, September 1 (Xinhua) -- The general price index of the
Tehran Stock Exchange Tuesday closed at 1525.86 points, up 8.07
points from Monday's finish.
</P>
<P>
The financial and industrial indexes rose respectively by 72.94
and 1.28 points to reach 4002.71 and 1266.66 points.
</P>
<P>
A total of 1,161,247 shares changed hands and the turnover was
3.89 billion rials (707,000 U.S. dollars).
</P>
<P>
The shares of 61 companies made gains while those of 6 others
declined. 
</P>
