according to local sources.
</P>
<P>
Seven people, including six Taiwan tourists, were killed in the
accident when the tourist bus in which they were riding was
involved in a head-on collision with a truck in Jiuquan Prefecture
near the Dunhuang Cave on August 22.
</P>
