Yangtze River has been at least in part attributed to
deforestation in the upper reaches of the river.
</P>
<P>
Concerned local teenagers have participated in various kinds of
activities to promote environmental protection, including
participating in environmental studies, promoting environmental
protection in heavily forested areas, and conducting surveys of
factories, lakes and forests. 
