<HEADLINE> Shenyang International Trade Fair Opens </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
SHENYANG, September 2 (Xinhua) -- The annual Shenyang
International Trade Fair opened here this morning in this capital
city of northeast China's Liaoning Province.
</P>
<P>
Sponsored by the China Council for Promotion of International
Trade (CCPIT) and eight cities in Liaoning Province, the trade
fair has attracted over 3,000 overseas participants from some 50
countries and regions.
</P>
<P>
